'''Veronica Ryder''' (born 1967) is an American truck driver and animal activist. She was the owner of [[Joy (cat)|Joy]], a Himalayan cat, who shared a loving relationship with her, unlike her late husband, [[Lil Mountjoy]]. 

==Early life==
Veronica was born in Massachustts. Her parents worked as healthcare professionals, specializing in animal care. Her father was a Vietnam draft dodger and came close to going to jail during Veronica's infancy.

